metadata.name: CC0lab Mixtape Vol. 1 1
metadata.description:
By minting one of our NFTs, you can become part of the CC0lab journey. Once 77 are minted, we will unlock the stems to songs in the mixtape.

6- Erix - Dontmesswithjuan, Shamanic, Michael Onabolu (12:16)
